reviewText: Item received quickly and as described.

So I'm loving all of Tonya's DVDs.  I had the pleasure of working out with her personally and bought these when she moved away.  I was used to her tough Body Pump class but this Trim & Toned surprised me!  It is a great workout and the ball makes gives it a different intensity.  I definitely see changes in my body and I love it!  Forget 20 minutes....once you start, you don't want to stop.  I do the entire DVD each time!
